### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### Workflow V2 API (Coze-style DAG Engine)
### Base URL: api/v2/workflows
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

@host = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@contentType = application/json

### ── Step 1: Login to get JWT token ──
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### CRUD Operations
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── Create Workflow ──
# @name createWorkflow
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "安全扫描流程",
  "description": "自动化安全扫描与告警工作流",
  "mode": 0
}

###
@workflowId = {{createWorkflow.response.body.data.id}}

### ── List Workflows (paged) ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&keyword=安全
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── List Published Workflows (paged) ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/published?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Get Workflow Detail ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Update Metadata ──
PUT {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/meta
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "安全扫描流程 v2",
  "description": "更新后的安全扫描工作流"
}

### ── Save Draft (Canvas JSON) ──
PUT {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/draft
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "canvasJson": "{\"nodes\":[{\"key\":\"entry_1\",\"type\":1,\"label\":\"开始\",\"config\":{},\"layout\":{\"x\":100,\"y\":100,\"width\":120,\"height\":60}},{\"key\":\"text_1\",\"type\":15,\"label\":\"文本处理\",\"config\":{\"template\":\"扫描结果: {{scan_target}}\",\"outputKey\":\"text_output\"},\"layout\":{\"x\":300,\"y\":100,\"width\":120,\"height\":60}},{\"key\":\"exit_1\",\"type\":2,\"label\":\"结束\",\"config\":{},\"layout\":{\"x\":500,\"y\":100,\"width\":120,\"height\":60}}],\"connections\":[{\"sourceNodeKey\":\"entry_1\",\"sourcePort\":\"output\",\"targetNodeKey\":\"text_1\",\"targetPort\":\"input\",\"condition\":null},{\"sourceNodeKey\":\"text_1\",\"sourcePort\":\"output\",\"targetNodeKey\":\"exit_1\",\"targetPort\":\"input\",\"condition\":null}]}",
  "commitId": "draft-001"
}

### ── Publish Workflow ──
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/publish
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "changeLog": "首次发布"
}

### ── List Versions ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Diff Two Versions ──
# fromId/toId 为版本表的 Id 字段（非 VersionNumber）
@fromVersionId = 1
@toVersionId = 2
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions/{{fromVersionId}}/diff/{{toVersionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Rollback to Version ──
@rollbackVersionId = 1
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions/{{rollbackVersionId}}/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{loginAdmin.response.headers.X-CSRF-TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

### ── Copy Workflow ──
# @name copyWorkflow
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/copy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@copiedId = {{copyWorkflow.response.body.data.id}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### Execution Operations
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── Sync Run ──
# @name runWorkflow
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "inputsJson": "{\"scan_target\":\"192.168.1.0/24\"}"
}

###
@executionId = {{runWorkflow.response.body.data.executionId}}

### ── SSE Stream Run ──
# 事件顺序示例：
# execution_start -> node_start -> node_output -> node_complete -> execution_complete
# 失败场景会返回 node_failed + execution_failed
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/stream
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "inputsJson": "{\"scan_target\":\"10.0.0.0/8\"}"
}

### ── Get Execution Process ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Get Execution Checkpoint ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/checkpoint
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Get Node Execution Detail ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/nodes/text_1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Cancel Execution ──
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Resume Execution ──
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Recover Execution ──
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/recover
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Get Debug View ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/executions/{{executionId}}/debug-view
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Debug Single Node ──
# 返回 data.executionId，且服务端会写入完整节点输入/输出到执行记录，可通过 process/nodes 查询
# 需要权限：ai-workflow:debug
POST {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}/debug-node
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "nodeKey": "text_1",
  "inputsJson": "{\"scan_target\":\"example.com\"}"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### Node Types
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── List Node Types ──
GET {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/node-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### Cleanup
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── Delete Copied Workflow ──
DELETE {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{copiedId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── Delete Original Workflow ──
DELETE {{host}}/api/v2/workflows/{{workflowId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
